# =============================================================================
# .actrc - Act (GitHub Actions Local Runner) Configuration
# =============================================================================
# This file configures act for running GitHub Actions workflows locally.
# See: https://github.com/nektos/act
#
# Usage:
#   act                    # Run default event (push)
#   act push               # Run push event
#   act pull_request       # Run pull_request event
#   act -W .github/workflows/build.yml  # Run specific workflow
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Platform Image Mapping
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Map GitHub runners to Docker images
# Using catthehacker images which are more compatible with act

# Medium-sized runner (recommended for most use cases)
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest

# For better compatibility with TeXLive, uncomment:
# -P ubuntu-latest=texlive/texlive:latest-full

# Large runner with more tools (slower to pull, ~17GB)
# -P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:full-latest

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Architecture
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# For Apple Silicon (M1/M2) Macs, uncomment:
# --container-architecture linux/amd64

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Artifact Handling
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Directory for workflow artifacts
--artifact-server-path /tmp/act-artifacts

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Secrets
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Load secrets from .secrets file (create this file locally, add to .gitignore)
# Format: KEY=value (one per line)
# --secret-file .secrets

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment Variables
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Pass environment variables to workflows
# --env KEY=value

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Other Options
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Verbose output (uncomment for debugging)
# --verbose

# Dry run - show what would execute without running
# -n

# Reuse containers between runs (faster)
# --reuse

# =============================================================================
# End of .actrc
# =============================================================================
